OL,3,CEnd of working from home? Your rights
OL,4,Cto flexible working explained
OL,6,FA growing number of employers are
OL,7,Fasking their staff to return to
OL,8,Fworking in the office as companies
OL,9,Fedge further away from post-Covid
OL,10,Fattitudes.
OL,12,FWorking from home has become a popular
OL,13,Fchoice for millions of people around
OL,14,Fthe United Kingdom, with many now used
OL,15,Fto a hybrid model.
OL,17,FSo, with a return to the office being
OL,18,Fmooted in a number of industries, what
OL,19,Fare your rights if you wish to submit
OL,20,Fa flexible working request?
