OL,6,FITV News spoke to an employment law
OL,7,Fexpert to answer the key questions.
OL,9,FWhat are the rights of an employee?
OL,11,FEarlier this year, all employees in
OL,12,FEngland, Wales and Scotland gained the
OL,13,Flegal right to request flexible
OL,14,Fworking. Different flexible working
OL,15,Frules exist in Northern Ireland.
OL,17,FConsequently, all employees have the
OL,18,Flegal right to request flexible
OL,19,Fworking, and can ask for a change to
OL,20,Fthe following:
