OL,3,CEnd of working from home? Your rights
OL,4,Cto flexible working explained
OL,6,FWhat must an employer do?
OL,8,FEmployers are required to deal with a
OL,9,Fflexible working request in a
OL,10,F"reasonable manner", according to .
OL,12,FFor example, this could include
OL,13,Fevaluating the pros and cons of an
OL,14,Fapplication, or discussing potential
OL,15,Falternatives to a request.
OL,17,FKaren Baxter, an employment law
OL,18,Fpartner, told ITV News that an
OL,19,Femployer has two months to reach an
OL,20,Foutcome "unless a longer period is
OL,21,Fagreed".
