OL,6,FCan you appeal a decision?
OL,8,FMs Baxter said it is possible to bring
OL,9,Fa complaint to an employment tribunal
OL,10,Fwhen contending that your "flexible
OL,11,Fworking request hasn't been properly
OL,12,Fconsidered, the employer hasn't
OL,13,Ffollowed the process or has relied on
OL,14,Fan unfair reason to reject my request".
OL,16,FEmployees can take an employer to a
OL,17,Ftribunal hearing if the latter does
OL,18,Fnot handle a request in a reasonable
OL,19,Fmanner.
